termit
------------------------------------------
Terminal emulator based on VTE library with Lua scripting

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.8.0-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.50.3-1
  libgtk3_0-3.22.15-1
  libintl8-0.19.8.1-2
  libpango1.0_0-1.40.6-1
  libvte2.91_0-0.46.2-1
  libX11_6-1.6.5-1
  lua-5.2.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.25-4
  cmake-3.6.2-1
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-5.4.0-1
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/nonstop/termit

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/nonstop/termit/archive/termit-3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack termit-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./termit-3.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/termit-3.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/termit-3.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(termit)
  /etc/xdg/termit/colormaps.lua
  /etc/xdg/termit/rc.lua
  /etc/xdg/termit/utils.lua
  /usr/bin/termit.exe
  /usr/share/appdata/termit.appdata.xml
  /usr/share/applications/termit.desktop
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/termit.README
  /usr/share/doc/termit/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/termit/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/termit/README
  /usr/share/doc/termit/TODO
  /usr/share/doc/termit/lua_api.txt
  /usr/share/doc/termit/rc.lua.example
  /usr/share/locale/de/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
  /usr/share/locale/es/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
  /usr/share/locale/fr/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
  /usr/share/locale/hu/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
  /usr/share/locale/ja/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
  /usr/share/locale/ko/LC_MESSAGES/termit.mo
